<template>
  <v-list>
    <v-list-group v-for="(group, index) in groups" :key="index" :value="true">
      <template v-slot:activator>
        <v-list-item-title>
          {{ group.name }}
        </v-list-item-title>
      </template>
      <v-list-item v-for="(calendar, i) in group.calendars" :key="i">
        <v-list-item-content>
          {{ calendar.name }}
        </v-list-item-content>
        <v-list-item-action>
          <v-list v-if="calendar.users.length > 0">
            <v-list-item v-for="(user, j) in calendar.users" :key="j">
              {{ user.name }}
            </v-list-item>
          </v-list>
        </v-list-item-action>
      </v-list-item>
    </v-list-group>
  </v-list>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      groups: [
        {
          name: 'Group 1',
          calendars: [
            {
              name: 'Calendar 1',
              users: [
                { name: 'User A' },
                { name: 'User B' },
              ],
            },
            {
              name: 'Calendar 2',
              users: [
                { name: 'User C' },
                { name: 'User D' },
              ],
            },
          ],
        },
        {
          name: 'Group 2',
          calendars: [
            {
              name: 'Calendar 3',
              users: [
                { name: 'User E' },
                { name: 'User F' },
              ],
            },
            {
              name: 'Calendar 4',
              users: [],
            },
          ],
        },
      ],
    };
  },
};
</script>
